  <entry>
    <title>Hexo添加分类和标签</title>
    <link href="http://smilewayto.top/wiki/hexo-tian-jia-fen-lei-he-biao-qian/"/>
    <id>http://smilewayto.top/wiki/hexo-tian-jia-fen-lei-he-biao-qian/</id>
    <published>2022-05-01T10:00:36.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-05-01T14:04:00.324Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="1-创建分类选项"><a href="#1-创建分类选项" class="headerlink" title="1.创建分类选项"></a>1.创建分类选项</h2><h3 id="1-1-生成“分类”页"><a href="#1-1-生成“分类”页" class="headerlink" title="1.1 生成“分类”页"></a>1.1 生成“分类”页</h3><p>进入博客所在文件夹。<br>执行命令 <code>hexo new page categories</code> 成功后会在./source/categories文件夹下生成文件 index.md<br><span id="more"></span><br>打开后默认内容是：<br><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: categories</span><br><span class="line">date: 2022-05-01 18:00:36</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>添加<code>type: &quot;categories&quot; layout: &quot;categories&quot;</code>,效果如下：<br><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: categories</span><br><span class="line">date: 2022-05-01 18:00:36</span><br><span class="line">type: &quot;categories&quot;</span><br><span class="line">layout: &quot;categories&quot;</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h3 id="1-2-给文章添加分类"><a href="#1-2-给文章添加分类" class="headerlink" title="1.2 给文章添加分类"></a>1.2 给文章添加分类</h3><p>执行命令  <code>hexo new &quot;文章名&quot;</code>  生成文章，打开后添加categories属性，添加分类格式如下：<br><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: Hexo添加分类和标签</span><br><span class="line">toc: true</span><br><span class="line">date: 2022-05-01 18:00:36</span><br><span class="line">tags:</span><br><span class="line">- Hexo</span><br><span class="line">categories:</span><br><span class="line">- Hexo</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br><code>-Hexo</code>表示文章属于“Hexo”这个分类。<br>Hexo中文章只能属于一个分类，如果添加两个分类，如：<br><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">categories:</span><br><span class="line">-Hexo</span><br><span class="line">-分类方法</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>Hexo不会产生两个分类，而是会将文章归类为Hexo这个大分类下的“分类方法”分类中。</p><h2 id="2-创建标签选项"><a href="#2-创建标签选项" class="headerlink" title="2 创建标签选项"></a>2 创建标签选项</h2><h3 id="2-1-生成“标签”页"><a href="#2-1-生成“标签”页" class="headerlink" title="2.1 生成“标签”页"></a>2.1 生成“标签”页</h3><p>进入博客所在文件夹。<br>执行命令  <code>hexo new page tags</code>  成功后会在./source/tags文件夹下生成文件 index.md<br>打开后默认内容为：<br><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: tags</span><br><span class="line">date: 2022-05-01 18:00:36</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>添加<code>type: &quot;tags&quot; layout: &quot;tags&quot;</code>,效果如下：<br><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: tags</span><br><span class="line">date: 2022-05-01 18:00:36</span><br><span class="line">type: &quot;tags&quot;</span><br><span class="line">layout: &quot;tags&quot;</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h3 id="2-2-给文章添加标签"><a href="#2-2-给文章添加标签" class="headerlink" title="2.2 给文章添加标签"></a>2.2 给文章添加标签</h3><p>执行命令  <code>hexo new &quot;文章名&quot;</code>  生成文章，打开后添加tags属性，添加标签格式如下：<br><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: Hexo添加分类和标签</span><br><span class="line">toc: true</span><br><span class="line">date: 2022-05-01 18:00:36</span><br><span class="line">tags:</span><br><span class="line">- Hexo</span><br><span class="line">categories:</span><br><span class="line">- Hexo</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>标签可以添加多个。</p><h2 id="参考资料"><a href="#参考资料" class="headerlink" title="参考资料"></a>参考资料</h2><blockquote><ul><li><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/cflsup/article/details/123452683">Hexo添加分类和标签</a></li></ul></blockquote>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;h2 id=&quot;1-创建分类选项&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#1-创建分类选项&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;1.创建分类选项&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;1.创建分类选项&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id=&quot;1-1-生成“分类”页&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#1-1-生成“分类”页&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;1.1 生成“分类”页&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;1.1 生成“分类”页&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;进入博客所在文件夹。&lt;br&gt;执行命令 &lt;code&gt;hexo new page categories&lt;/code&gt; 成功后会在./source/categories文件夹下生成文件 index.md&lt;br&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
